Global Ultrathin Portables (Ultrabooks and MacBook Air) Market Insights
Ultrathin Portables (Ultrabooks and MacBook Air) Market size was valued at USD 30 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 50 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.4% from 2024 to 2030.

Ultrathin Portables (Ultrabooks and MacBook Air) Market Overview
The global ultrathin portable market, which includes ultrabooks and MacBook Air devices, is experiencing significant growth. In 2024, the market was valued at approximately USD 35 billion, with expectations to expand at a CAGR of 9% over the forecast period (2025-2030). This growth is driven by consumer demand for lightweight, powerful, and long-lasting devices. Ultrabooks and MacBook Airs cater to professionals, students, and casual users seeking portability without compromising performance. Their growing popularity in both personal and business applications contributes to the expanding market. The demand for ultrathin laptops is particularly high in regions like North America, Europe, and Asia-Pacific, as they are seen as a balance between productivity and portability. With innovations in battery technology and processor efficiency, these devices continue to evolve, providing users with an enhanced experience.

